Uttar Pradesh
Aug 29, 2014
Abuse
Description:
			A 30-year-old woman was allegedly raped by two men from Muzaffarnagar when she came here to hunt for a house.

The two accused, Gaurav Tyagi and Yogesh Kumar, chased the woman on Wednesday and drugged her with sedatives, following which they raped her in Jafrabad area here. The woman was later thrown to an isolated area in Hapur, they said.

A case was registered against the accused after the woman lodged a complaint against the duo at Lalkurti Thana, police said, adding efforts are being made to arrest them.


